{"tid":970807,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲高爾認定冠軍只餘3隊之爭　讚高普令利物浦鬥心勝曼城","createTime":"2019-01-06T06:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T03:12:51.000Z","uid":19889,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb546433283c0a14c84c27f0e6120f22ba97081","tid":970807,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2290708/org/739f921459407db1347210a0f034f10a.jpg/Hbe0gczKn9pDsA2hgg5lX2fPvfG5Wr5jF-5WoRfuVqE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2290708%2Forg%2F739f921459407db1347210a0f034f10a.jpg%2FHbe0gczKn9pDsA2hgg5lX2fPvfG5Wr5jF-5WoRfuVqE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=df606379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英超已過半，利物浦以4分領前曼城，連前曼聯主帥雲高爾（Louis van Gaal）也認為利物浦在高普帶領下充滿決心，睇好利物浦首奪英超。<br />\n<br />\n前曼聯主帥雲高爾（Louis van Gaal）2014至2016年執教曼聯，離開前為紅魔贏得英格蘭足總盃，這名荷蘭教練在訪問中認為英超冠軍是三隊之爭，分別是利物浦、曼城和熱刺，沒提到曼聯的名字。<br />\n<br />\n即使利物浦在上輪英超以1︰2負曼城，但仍在榜首以4分帶前，雲高雲從兩雄交鋒之中看到曼城的不足︰「這場賽事證明曼城不能防守，當利物浦追平一刻，曼城實有足夠的防守球員在禁區內。曼城在英超往往OUTPLAY對手，因此常常不用防守，但面對強隊如利物浦，就反映出曼城防守時很混亂。」雲帥澄清很享受看曼城比賽，但高普為利物浦所做的事非同凡享。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2290564/org/75a1ad11c80b1738c8537dfdb856af22.jpg/u9xttnABLSfuTI9oIVlJaZlU0Fe1MJh36_TP9uv0z_Y?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2290564%2Forg%2F75a1ad11c80b1738c8537dfdb856af22.jpg%2Fu9xttnABLSfuTI9oIVlJaZlU0Fe1MJh36_TP9uv0z_Y%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9c931a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲高爾相信曼城球員質素較利物浦佳，不過高普在執教功力更勝一籌，可力壓哥迪奧拿助利物浦首奪英超錦標︰「高普把利物浦轉化為戰鬥機器，不論進攻及防守方面，<span style=\"color: red;\">若我要下注（英超冠軍），利物浦是我的選擇</span>。利物浦並不擁有最高水平的球員，最高水平的在曼城，但同時這正是哥迪奧拿的弱點，一如以往，他只調教球隊的進攻。曼城需要防守時很不滯，利物浦防守能力更佳。」<br />\n<br />\n他舉例指法明奴、文尼及沙拿跑動極多，兼顧防守、反擊及創造，全隊爭勝的決心比曼城大，「高普令利物浦不論控球或無球時都具競爭力，正是哥迪奧拿球隊所缺乏的事，曼城的足球意念及踢法很好，不過沒有正確的戰鬥精神。」<br />\n<br />\n利物浦之後的英超賽事對手實力不強，至2月24日作客曼聯。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/279270/%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85-%E9%9B%B2%E9%AB%98%E7%88%BE%E8%AA%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%AA%E9%A4%983%E9%9A%8A%E4%B9%8B%E7%88%AD-%E8%AE%9A%E9%AB%98%E6%99%AE%E4%BB%A4%E5%88%A9%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%A6%E9%AC%A5%E5%BF%83%E5%8B%9D%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F279270%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E9%259B%25B2%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%258F%25AA%25E9%25A4%25983%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2588%25AD-%25E8%25AE%259A%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B5%25A6%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%258B%259D%25E6%259B%25BC%25E5%259F%258E&d=X4%2FzfWi5cbJ7qy%2BCoL4PzUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=f86d797f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/279270/%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85-%E9%9B%B2%E9%AB%98%E7%88%BE%E8%AA%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%AA%E9%A4%983%E9%9A%8A%E4%B9%8B%E7%88%AD-%E8%AE%9A%E9%AB%98%E6%99%AE%E4%BB%A4%E5%88%A9%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%A6%E9%AC%A5%E5%BF%83%E5%8B%9D%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E</a>"},{"pid":"a988da31a47f1ea74511f3d11fbb1c40388aae31","tid":970807,"uid":44457,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"熱浦城爭冠"},{"pid":"9c96bd8e4cbcca57dfeeed267816d06ae8dfa092","tid":970807,"uid":224966,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"曼聯後上緊"},{"pid":"fb44ac808875c51d51582fc747b778fea3b8bc6d","tid":970807,"uid":69568,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"hk01 唔識譯outplay?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fefde600aa2ae022e88ce71d1f6613d9f9c8130","tid":970807,"uid":127177,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fb44ac808875c51d51582fc747b778fea3b8bc6d","tid":970807,"uid":69568,"like":6,"dis